What are you doing?

18
00:01:41,733 --> 00:01:45,200
Pull yourself together, Na Young Won.

19
00:01:46,366 --> 00:01:48,566
Sir, congratulations.

20
00:01:49,466 --> 00:01:50,233
What?

21
00:01:50,233 --> 00:01:52,866
Damyung Construction called to tell me

22
00:01:52,866 --> 00:01:54,598
they're accepting your investment.

23
00:01:54,599 --> 00:01:56,467
That's a relief.

24
00:01:56,467 --> 00:02:00,331
You put so much time and effort into it. I thought you'd be ecstatic.

25
00:02:00,331 --> 00:02:02,633
Is something wrong?

26
00:02:02,633 --> 00:02:04,366
No.

27
00:02:05,032 --> 00:02:07,433
Everything's fine.

28
00:02:11,533 --> 00:02:13,265
Hello, Editor Nam?

29
00:02:13,266 --> 00:02:16,232
Why are you calling when you should be at work?

30
00:02:16,232 --> 00:02:18,465
What? An outside meeting?

31
00:02:18,465 --> 00:02:19,732
Oh, okay.

32
00:02:19,733 --> 00:02:22,266
Don't be late for our meeting. Bye.

33
00:02:22,266 --> 00:02:24,830
Where's the material...

34
