What's all this? Well?

35
00:02:34,050 --> 00:02:35,790

36
00:02:35,790 --> 00:02:37,360
Yook Mi Ra!

37
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:39,690

38
00:02:39,699 --> 00:02:42,599
How can you eat and sleep at the office?

39
00:02:42,599 --> 00:02:45,131
This is Monthly Magazine Home, not Yook Mi Ra's home.

40
00:02:45,132 --> 00:02:47,399
She said it was because she couldn't pay rent.

41
00:02:47,399 --> 00:02:49,767
Still, this is unacceptable.

42
00:02:51,232 --> 00:02:52,400
How long has it been?

43
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:54,065
About two months...

44
00:02:54,065 --> 00:02:56,099
What? That long?

45
00:02:56,099 --> 00:02:57,698
Weren't you scared?

46
00:02:57,698 --> 00:02:59,032
It's dangerous, being all alone.

47
00:02:59,032 --> 00:03:00,899
I was going to get a new place soon.

48
00:03:00,899 --> 00:03:02,732
Yes, get a new place quickly.

49
00:03:02,733 --> 00:03:05,567
- Before the CEO finds out... 
 - Stop.

50
00:03:05,567 --> 00:03:09,066
Why are you all chatting and not working?

51
00:03:09,066 --> 00:03:10,167
Oh, sir.

52
00:03:10,167 --> 00:03:12,499
We were about to start working.

53
00:03:12,499 --> 00:03:14,331
Focus on your jobs.

54
00:03:14,331 --> 00:03:17,399
