55
00:03:17,399 --> 00:03:19,630
I'm sorry.

56
00:03:21,933 --> 00:03:24,400
I guess he didn't hear.

57
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:26,732
You're lucky the CEO didn't catch you.

58
00:03:26,732 --> 00:03:27,667
Right.

59
00:03:27,668 --> 00:03:31,565
If he did, knowing him, he would've told you to pay

60
00:03:31,565 --> 00:03:33,566
for the electricity and water you used.

61
00:03:33,566 --> 00:03:35,833
Get a new place right now, okay?

62
00:03:35,833 --> 00:03:37,232
Yes, sir.

63
00:03:37,232 --> 00:03:39,990
I'm really sorry.

64
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:54,266
Are you all right?

65
00:03:54,266 --> 00:03:55,033
Yes.

66
00:03:55,033 --> 00:03:57,165
You should've told me.

67
00:03:57,165 --> 00:03:59,065
Come live with me until you find a new place.

68
00:03:59,065 --> 00:04:01,566
I didn't tell you because I knew you'd say that.

69
00:04:01,566 --> 00:04:02,833
What?

70
00:04:02,833 --> 00:04:05,266
I didn't want you to worry about me.

71
00:04:05,266 --> 00:04:07,166
Come on.

72
00:04:07,166 --> 00:04:10,832
Then is it okay to live here, always nervous?

73
00:04:12,299 --> 00:04:14,700
It must've been hard.

74
00:04:14,700 --> 00:04:19,333
But I was able to save up on rent.

75
00:04:19,333 --> 00:04:23,832
The rent in Seoul is atrocious.

76
00:04:23,832 --> 00:04:26,067
True.

77
00:04:26,067 --> 00:04:27,999
Rent is one thing.

78
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:31,865
So much time is wasted on the commute.

79
00:04:31,865 --> 00:04:35,599
I wanted to use that time to focus on my job.

80
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:39,132
I want to become a great editor like you quickly.

81
00:04:39,132 --> 00:04:40,199
What?

82
00:04:40,200 --> 00:04:41,665
I told you.

83
00:04:41,666 --> 00:04:45,640
You are my role model.

84
00:04:53,400 --> 00:04:55,232
How's the interior design article coming along?

85
00:04:55,232 --> 00:04:58,064
How about indirectly experiencing remodeling in VR?

86
00:04:58,064 --> 00:04:59,233
People in their twenties and thirties...

87
00:04:59,233 --> 00:04:59,932
 Only by words?

88
00:04:59,932 --> 00:05:01,965
 Set me up with someone, you, Nam Sang Soon!

89
00:05:01,965 --> 00:05:05,020
 Huh? Set me up.

90
00:05:09,399 --> 00:05:10,999
 What was that?

91
00:05:10,999 --> 00:05:14,600
 My heart was pounding like crazy.

92
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,233
 Do I...?

93
00:05:16,233 --> 00:05:19,331
I think this is a good time to cover that.

94
00:05:19,331 --> 00:05:21,365
 No. That doesn't make sense.

95
00:05:21,365 --> 00:05:22,500
What do you think, Editor Nam?

96
00:05:22,501 --> 00:05:24,298
It doesn't make sense.

97
00:05:24,298 --> 00:05:26,599
- What? 
 - What?

98
00:05:26,599 --> 00:05:28,931
- Why does it not make sense? 
 - What?

99
00:05:28,931 --> 00:05:32,266
- You just said that it doesn't make sense. 
 - I did?

100
00:05:32,266 --> 00:05:33,798
Yes, you did.

101
00:05:33,798 --> 00:05:38,166
Jeez, Editor Nam. Focus on the meeting!

102
00:05:41,899 --> 00:05:44,699
I... I... I... I'm sorry.

103
00:05:44,699 --> 00:05:46,832
I need to go to the bathroom.

104
00:05:50,267 --> 00:05:52,332
What's up with that fool?

105
00:05:52,332 --> 00:05:54,432
The installment payment's been settled. What is it now?

106
00:05:54,433 --> 00:05:55,832
I know.

107
00:05:55,832 --> 00:05:59,890
Why is he so out of it?

108
00:06:14,133 --> 00:06:16,064
What is wrong with me?

109
00:06:16,064 --> 00:06:17,865
No way...

110
00:06:19,267 --> 00:06:22,540
It's not true, right, Sang Soon?

111
00:06:24,333 --> 00:06:26,332
Of course, it's not.

112
00:06:38,132 --> 00:06:42,434
 I want to become a great editor like you quickly.

113
00:06:42,434 --> 00:06:46,367
 You're my role model.

114
00:06:48,333 --> 00:06:50,333
I'm ashamed.

115
00:06:52,065 --> 00:06:55,134
Any human being should be ashamed.

116
00:06:57,100 --> 00:07:00,360
Pull it together for real.

117
