The survey result shows 83% of young people aren't satisfied

133
00:08:32,899 --> 00:08:34,498
with where they live.

134
00:08:34,498 --> 00:08:39,498
To find out why I want to investigate their residences.

135
00:08:39,498 --> 00:08:41,866
You did a lot of research.

136
00:08:41,866 --> 00:08:43,899
It won't be difficult to get a source.

137
00:08:43,899 --> 00:08:45,532
Our assistants volunteered to help.

138
00:08:45,533 --> 00:08:47,800
It'll be meaningful and entertaining.

139
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:48,799
Isn't it perfect?

140
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:52,400
What use is it if it's perfect?

141
00:08:53,132 --> 00:08:54,400
It won't make money.

142
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:55,265
What?

143
00:08:55,266 --> 00:08:58,531
We should cover captivating, luxurious homes

144
00:08:58,531 --> 00:09:00,331
and stick more ads after them.

145
00:09:00,331 --> 00:09:03,299
What's this? Jeez.

146
00:09:03,299 --> 00:09:04,865
Right, sir? I did well, right?

147
00:09:04,865 --> 00:09:06,699
No. Proceed with the story.

148
00:09:06,700 --> 00:09:08,733
Get me more details.

149
00:09:08,734 --> 00:09:09,734
Really?

150
00:09:09,735 --> 00:09:11,499
This is clearly an article that doesn't make money.

151
00:09:11,500 --> 00:09:14,766
You're writing the article that makes money.

152
00:09:14,767 --> 00:09:16,631
This is to keep up our image.

153
00:09:16,632 --> 00:09:18,966
To not be considered a tabloid.

154
00:09:18,966 --> 00:09:22,200
You have such good judgment.

155
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:24,631
Then calmly carry it out, Editor Na.

156
00:09:24,632 --> 00:09:26,232
Okay.

157
00:09:33,099 --> 00:09:34,998
Here are the details you asked for.

158
00:09:34,998 --> 00:09:38,132
Thank you. You may leave.

159
00:09:39,165 --> 00:09:40,633
Sir.

160
00:09:40,633 --> 00:09:43,032
Thank you for permitting the special article.

161
00:09:43,033 --> 00:09:44,366
No need.

162
00:09:44,367 --> 00:09:48,300
As I said, it's to keep up our image.

163
00:09:48,300 --> 00:09:49,867
Okay.

164
00:09:50,599 --> 00:09:55,231
Also, I'd like to cancel what I said before.

165
00:09:57,600 --> 00:10:00,633
 That will never happen again.

166
00:10:00,633 --> 00:10:04,600
 But if I do something ridiculous like that,

167
00:10:07,299 --> 00:10:11,033
 please be cold to me like you are now.

168
00:10:11,033 --> 00:10:16,367
 That way, I won't have any lingering feelings.

169
00:10:19,432 --> 00:10:23,633
I think I made you more uncomfortable.

170
00:10:23,633 --> 00:10:26,360
Treat me however it makes you comfortable.

171
00:10:29,267 --> 00:10:32,067
It doesn't matter how you treat me.

172
00:10:32,067 --> 00:10:35,366
I don't think I'll have any lingering feelings anymore.

173
00:10:37,533 --> 00:10:38,970
Good day.

