00:11:32,566 --> 00:11:33,790
 A gift for you.

183
00:11:33,790 --> 00:11:40,390
♫  Leaving me behind here?  ♫

184
00:11:40,390 --> 00:11:44,370
 I don't think I'll have any lingering feelings anymore.

